{"tid":680636,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"1963年大旱重臨？天文台前台長林超英「今年恐怖好異常」","createTime":"2018-05-27T10:28:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-27T10:43:57.000Z","uid":52978,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"bef1f2fe8a3162b99970cb0abc0ea56f105b47f4","tid":680636,"uid":52978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T10:28:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180527/s00001/1527409670885\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180527%2Fs00001%2F1527409670885&d=JLNiTcM%2FumB9ObWVpLrhmgIBMskQiLF9ooRt%2FFIrCZo%3D&h=4f5e09b1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180527%2Fs00001%2F1527409670885&h=c8208d57\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180527/s00001/1527409670885</a><br />\n<br />\n本港近日持續酷熱，今日市區氣溫普遍32度以上，將軍澳更錄得34.7度高溫。林超英中午於無綫節目《講清講楚》中直言「有排捱」，因五月只是「初夏」，之後還有「盛夏」，故有機會愈來愈熱：「通常最熱是7月至8月，現在只是開始。」"},{"pid":"17fde5ecfcbee201c86cac7a94bdccd3d343ae9f","tid":680636,"uid":52978,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T10:29:27.000Z","msg":"林超英解釋，受太平洋高壓脊影響，五月天提早變成「盛夏」，形容「今年有些恐怖」：「現在的模樣（情況）應是7月出現&hellip;&hellip;其實是好異常的。高壓脊壓着香港，什麼雲也沒有&hellip;&hellip;對於中國內地來說，他們平時講梅雨，梅雨好像也不見了，驚驚地的。」"},{"pid":"aa8e5e124c7f924b082eae38bd1af81ba09218e3","tid":680636,"uid":52978,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T10:30:03.000Z","msg":"林超英表示，現時淡水湖「乾到見回舊時的村，這情況多年未見，加上內地東江流域一些水庫亦「乾到露出下面的村」，認為大家要留意這些徵兆：「旱情比較突出，不要掉以輕心。」"},{"pid":"6219c07acee3da9e15775a33de10a241d1a41775","tid":680636,"uid":52978,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T10:31:01.000Z","msg":"今年真係熱到核爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n想快d落場大雨，但睇完篇野，唔易"},{"pid":"b06e6076333